column2: SELECT u.up_name as name, &&&&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type, p.petroMag_u, p.petroMagErr_u, p.petroMag_g, p.petroMagErr_g, p.petroMag_r, p.petroMagErr_r,p.petroMag_i, p.petroMagErr_i, p.petroMag_z, p.petroMagErr_z FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID ORDER by x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
